<HEADLINE> Beijing Cracks Illegal Fund Raising Gang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua)-- Beijing court has dealt severely
with a major criminal gang who illegally raised over 500 million
yuan through various sorts of cheats.
</P>
<P>
Cao Yufei, Gong Congying and Gao Zhenyu squandered and diverted
some of the money and then fled the country with the rest.
</P>
<P>
Cao was sentenced to death, with Gong and Gao sentenced to
death on probation and life imprisonment respectively, in a court
proceeding today.
</P>
<P>
Chen Huifang and four other people, who assisted the above
mentioned three criminals to flee across the border, were
sentenced to two to eight years in prison.  
</P>
