<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Seventeen major Chinese
universities including the Chinese People's University, Shanghai
Jiaotong University and Fudan University, will get 6.95 billion
yuan in loans from the Industrial and Commercial Bank of China (
ICBC).
