<HEADLINE> China Holds Third International Camera Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua) -- The Third China Photograph and
Electrical Imaging Machinery and Technology Fair opened here today,
a major event expected to has an impetus to China's fast growing
camera industry.
</P>
<P>
