</P>
<P>
Producers of the upcoming Beijing performance gala released on
April 17 the playbill for the event scheduled for May 1 to 31.
</P>
<P>
More than 1,000 artists from 24 countries and regions will join
the largest-ever performance festival ever held in China, sources
with the China Performing Arts Agency (CPAA) said.
</P>
<P>
