mines. This was confirmed by experts from the Chinese People's
Liberation Army (PLA) and the United Nations who recently
inspected and studied the results of two rounds of large-scale
mine clearing operations carried out by the Chinese army along the
Sino-Vietnamese border during 1992-99.

