as at least four tornadoes hit Labette County in Kansas State, the
United States, said reports reaching here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Some houses were destroyed and many others damaged in tornadoes,
and damage to a theater, grocery store, car dealership and other
downtown businesses was also heavy in Parsons Town of the county,
according to the reports. (BC-US-Tornadoes)
