Cup after a 2-2 draw against Galatasaray in the semi-final at
Elland Road on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Trailing 2-0 from the first leg, the home side fell behind to a
fourth minute penalty from Gheorghe Hagi and never fully recovered
as a Turkish side reached the final of a major European
competition for the first time.
</P>
