<TEXT>
<P>
The SSN, a branch of the National Autonomous University of
Mexico (UNAM) Geophysics Institute said in its weekly report that
there was an earthquake in the coast of Guerrero State, at 02.43
with a magnitude of 3.9 degrees on Friday
</P>
<P>
